text: Kanzafarovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Kanzafarovsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 45 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Zilair, 4 km from Yumaguzhino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Kanzafarovo
